    <bodyTop>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>What is the nature of society and how can we change it for the better? This is the kind of sceptical question that you’ll learn how to ask, and answer, on this course. You will learn how to critique preconceptions about social equality and justice. You will embrace new ideas and schools of thought on this intellectually stimulating and personally empowering course. You will graduate ready to make a real difference to people’s lives.</p>]]></Value>
    </bodyTop>
